g.text: 1. User wants to log their food.
2. SYSTEM Asks if the entry relates to Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, or Snacks
3. User has entered all food events they wish to log
4. User chooses either Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, or Snacks
5. SYSTEM Ask what time the food was eaten.
8. SYSTEM Asks for a description/notes of what was eaten.
